org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.scopes

Interface IMutableDefinitionSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDefinitionSet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LargeDefinitionSet, SmallDefinitionSet

    public interface IMutableDefinitionSet
extends IDefinitionSet
    This interface extends IDefinitionSet to add mutation methods.

    It is implemented by SmallDefinitionSet and LargeDefinitionSet. However, a single IDefinition acts as its own IDefinitionSet of size 1, but is not a IMutableDefinitionSet.
